Antennomere 1 coniform (
Fig. 53
); all antennomeres concolorous; basal two-thirds of intervals 1-5 glabrous medially, with irregular setae laterally (
Fig. 81
); lamella of aedeagus subtruncate at apex (
Fig. 119
